below—let’s talk about it."', 'Posted', 'https://youtube.com/shorts/GTY0NXNJPHA?feature=share , https://www.instagram.com/reel/DZCXB2YCU4i/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&igsh=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==', '14:05', '⏳ Did you know? Your eggs are as old as you are.

