**[0:00–0:03] HOOK (🔴 OPEN LOOP 1)**
Strategy: Contrarian Hook

*"Everyone''s asking me which month is best to conceive.."*

*"Is it February — the month of love? April, so you have a January baby? Day 14 because every aunty, every app said so? None of that is actually the point."*

*"Because here''s what I see after 20 years — couples miss their actual window by sometimes just two or three days. There''s no magic month. But there IS a magic window. The 5 days before ovulation and the day of. That''s it. And if your cycle is 26 days, or 32 days, day 14 is probably wrong for you. You''re missing it completely — and blaming yourself for something that was never your fault."*

*"What actually matters is tracking ovulation with LH strips or a scan, look for clear cervical mucus, time intimacy every other day in that window. Not one perfect night you''ve been stressing about for weeks. Every other day, in the window. That''s basically it. And when you do that, your chances go up not because the stars aligned, but because you finally had the right information.So stop asking which month. Start asking which day — honestly, that''s the whole thing. Questions about your cycle or timing? DM us or call Janya Fertility — HSR Layout, Bengaluru."*', 'Pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'No', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'migration');
